				I solo'd the warden it was fairly easy for me as a 39 bard.  First I charmed a mob and sent it in to attack the Warden and trigger the Guards to spawn.  I would suggest something that can take a few hits to slow up the Warden while you are pulling the guards away.  After I pulled the guards to the zone I tracked down the Warden again and started charming anything I could get my hands on and throwing them at the warden till he was dead.  I liked the  frost giant femur even though it is only usable by large races.  Made a good gift to a shaman friend o mine.  I am not sure what happened to the guards or wether the guards despawned or what,  I do know however they are highly resistant to magic of all kinds,  nothing I threw at them stuck.<BR>
